This is my collection of vim scripts and tools. It is distributed with the
dowhateveryouwantware license. In order to install them, follow the
instructions below:

If you are using Ubuntu/Debian/Mint, make sure you have these packages
installed: build-essential curl libclang1 libpython-dev
For other distributions you need to check the equivalent packages

Copy vim initialization file to your home directory
$cp vimrc ~/.vimrc
Copy vim configuration files directory to your home directory
$cp vim ~/.vim

Open vim or gvim
Execute ":PlugInstall"
Wait until all software is installed
Close vim/gvim and open it again

Caciano Machado <caciano.machado@ufrgs.br>
